text:
Gawwwds!!!!
What a person and what a talent. Padhai, gaana aur ab to party(xD) bhi kuch bhi karwalo har cheez mein chaapu. I wish we had bonded a bit earlier but "All's well that ends well". Are Hindu Sher to bolna hi bhul gaya. Itna mast laga tha ek Hindu Sher se milke. Same ideologies and same concerns(yaad hai first year ki debate with Yogi, gaand hi fat gayi thi gale ki lol). 
Bas gawds aage jaake bhul na jaana.
P.S: Ye jo final year mein evolve hue ho na aap, gaand fat gaya dekh ke. 
JSR
author: Akshat  Tiwari
